---
title: Creamy Chicken & Veggie Fusilli with Red Pesto & Parsley
description: We’re painting the pasta red, so make sure to stir that deliciously vibrant red pesto through the penne. To help it along is a creamy sauce with chicken and veggies to soak up the pesto and paint the perfect dinner time picture.

